text: Ti striharula'i aphna bubaharusita aphna choraharusita, ra aphna bha'iharusita, ra aphna bhatijaharusita, ra aphna bhanjiharusita, ra aphna melaka striharusita ra na uniharusita jasala'i uniharumathi svamitvako adhikara prapta cha parda nagarnuma kunai papa chaina. Striharu! Allahasita dara, niscaya nai allaha hareka kurako saksi cha
